OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK to borrow billions to   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcut energy bills           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Prime Minister Liz Truss is understood 
OL,6, to be planning to borrow billions to   
OL,7, limit the expected sharp rise in energy
OL,8, bills for households and firms.        
OL,10,FIt is understood that a typical energy 
OL,11,Fbill could be capped at around #2,500  
OL,12,Fwith full details expected on Thursday.
OL,14,FCurrently, a typical household's gas   
OL,15,Fand electricity bill is due to rise    
OL,16,Ffrom #1,971 to #3,549 in October.      
OL,18,FThe government's plans to subsidise    
OL,19,Fbills means that customers will not be 
OL,20,Fexpected to repay the support.         
